


translate English day4_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_a0f421cf:


    br "\n The mound is cold and well-packed. I stand atop it. I look around, and as I do, it causes mud to stick to my foot.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_3f811b55:


    extend "\nI pick up my foot and look at it. No... It's not mud. It's animal entrails. Something sticky, like pus, squirts out of the destroyed intestines beneath my heel.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_7fb90719:


    extend "\nCorpses litter the floor. From above me, lukewarm blood drips down onto me. It's like I'm inside someone's grave. This is a world I know."


translate English day4_9c4ebc06:



    nvl clear
    br "\n...Bump, bump, bump. A strange noise reaches my ears. A black shadow sways before my eyes. The warm, damp air tickles my skin.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_5e482c9e:


    extend "\nFlies. A whole swarm of flies is stuck to my arm. Underneath their pulsating mass, my arm is completely black.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_86ba49fc:


    extend "The small creatures tirelessly flap their wings as if to suck the life out of me--me, who is going to die."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_0f6813ae:


    br "\n Suddenly, something familiar and horrifying envolops all my senses. I look up. In the dark ceiling above, I can see an angel's halo.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_3c6400e9:


    extend "\nThe figure appears to be reaching out a hand for me. She's so beautiful it almost overwhelms my everything.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_98f881e4:


    extend "\nReverence--what one must have as a person, along with an appropriate level of fear. The figure is brilliant, instilling all those emotions and more.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_a1e55336:


    extend "\nSuddenly, the angel is embracing me. She places a white hand on my abdomen. I quickly begin to sweat.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_e361806e:


    extend "\nBut I accept the hand nonetheless. She is someone I cannot resist--she is something I cannot simply brush off."


translate English day4_47382139:



    nvl clear
    br "\nThe black insects, still stuck to my filthy body, crawl onto her elegant, pure, stainless hand.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_9ee4f656:


    extend "\nShe appears unafraid, even smiling, as she gently whispers:{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_4039d88b:


    extend "\n\n\"If you need anything else...please tell me, okay?\"{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_468052c9:


    extend "\n\nEventually, the angel's face comes into sight.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_a636a1af:


    extend "\nIt's *her* face.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_b3ec82af:


    extend "\nI've met her before."


translate English day4_fc0d9337:


    br "\nWhen I come to, I stand beneath a familiar sky. {w}At my feet is a dragging, sucking, sticky muck. The rotten odor of entrails threatens to split my mind in two.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_51f81567:


    extend "\nBlood and flesh--I don't know whose--rain down from overhead. {w}It's a dream. {w}*That* dream.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_b28d4006:


    extend "\nThe dream of the angel. {w}Her frail arms embrace me tightly, as though trying to take me away from this dreadful view.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_2120e4b1:


    extend " My toes point dangerously towards the very edge of the cliff. I'm about to fall.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_9276ce3f:


    extend "\nI don't even remember how things came to this. {w}Breathing hard, I swallow, then sense a presence from behind.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_50de605a:


    extend " Hair tickles my cheek. Then, a soft breath that doesn't match this place ghosts across me.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_9954f808:


    extend "\nIt's an angel."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_fa7fe6a9:


    br "\nAn angel has caught me and won't let go. {w}My head won't move. I can't lift my arms.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_70de744d:


    extend "\nI rally every ounce of my strength, trying to kick the ground and flail my arms, but it only serves to further crush the blood and guts stuck to my shoes and clothing.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_db5f54da:


    extend "\nLight shines down, blinding me. A pure, blazing, white light. {w}The angel's wings unfurl, casting a shadow on me from overhead.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_ceee5f8c:


    extend "\nThe angel squeezes my body even more tightly--so tightly it feels like my organs will be crushed. {w}I feel both the warmth of the angel and a terrible, freezing chill down my spine.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_8d9aad5e:


    extend "\nThe angel looks down at my terrified face, then gently smiles."


translate English day4_80da8c9e:



    nvl clear
    br "\n \"Let go...!\"{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_5a25c86a:


    extend "\nI struggle, desperately trying to escape the angel, then finally shake free.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_849092fc:


    extend "\nEventually, the angel's face comes into sight.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_a636a1af_1:


    extend "\nIt's *her* face.{w}{nw}"


translate English day4_48882ecd:


    extend "\nAnd I've met her somewhere before... haven't I?"


translate English day4_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_57e20c0d:


    hk "Okay, everyone! Let's all keep on loving one another as we work today!"


translate English day4_35134e7c:


    nar "Only one or two people respond through the din."


translate English day4_6e7eb212:


    nar "With the main bishop's morning greeting finished, Securett gives a silent bow. The morning starts the same way as always."


translate English day4_1e2d1ad5:


    sc "Wait here until I return. Don't do anything. Today's job will be difficult for newcomers, so prepare yourselves."


translate English day4_6c6bf8bb:


    nar "Securett follows Bishop Haku out. "


translate English day4_6945e5df:


    nar "Before I can ask about it, Securett disappears at the end of the passage. He's always like that."


translate English day4_7897188a:


    nar "Without much other choice, I sit in the room with Maya--the other newcomer--and decide to wait for him."


translate English day4_b9ea354a:


    my "I wonder what Cue is always doing with the bishop..."


translate English day4_f1155a26:


    pl "Paperwork maybe?"


translate English day4_5da6b56e:


    my "I think he has it pretty hard... He has to do his regular department work while helping with the bishop's work, doesn't he?"


translate English day4_8b3fe205:


    pl "Yeah. He's one of those, er, auxiliary bishops, apparently. "


translate English day4_59102e4f:


    pl "Though I don't really know why he takes on all these painful tasks either..."


translate English day4_de295e7c:


    nar "In all honesty, I don't know much at all about auxiliary bishops. Dr. Grette gave me a basic rundown yesterday, but that's all."


translate English day4_81605afb:


    nar "Even so, I said the word since it came to mind. I probably don't want to cut off my conversation with Maya."


translate English day4_7b81bf6b:


    my "Hmm. I don't think that's it... It's more like he's just always with the bishop. "


translate English day4_f2b4a081:


    my "And she's a little difficult to get used to..."


translate English day4_bc55487b:


    pl "You thought the same too, huh?"


translate English day4_cb627505:


    my "Huh?"


translate English day4_03f8703b:


    pl "Doesn't the bishop seem kind of weird sometimes? Like... Her face will suddenly go all serious in the middle of a conversation..."


translate English day4_d2d3cd52:


    pl "But she doesn't really do it, it just feels like she does."


translate English day4_6c522113:


    my "Yeah..."


translate English day4_e7724ae0:


    pl "It's kind of... ominous, I guess."


translate English day4_8f2d4f38:


    my "Yeah... Maybe..."


translate English day4_f429d4f7:


    pl "...Probably not a good idea to say stuff like that without thinking."


translate English day4_55c7ead9:


    my "I don't know, she just... She's slow at talking, but I don't get a bad feeling from her or an ominous one, either..."


translate English day4_afb346cf:


    pl "R-Really?"


translate English day4_19400eab:


    my "Maybe you're just oversensitive?"


translate English day4_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day4_dce0e583:


    my "...[na2], did something happen?"


translate English day4_6b6237a7:


    pl "Huh? What?"


translate English day4_9287c3ef:


    nar "To be honest, I'd be lying to her if I said I didn't recall anything that had to do with the blonde-haired girl. "


translate English day4_e50f4847:


    nar "I wish I could tell her nothing happened, but for some reason, my mouth doesn't want to open."


translate English day4_dae6521e:


    nar "The awkward silence continues until she says something."


translate English day4_0c18e6e8:


    my "...If it's nothing, then that's fine."


translate English day4_df535d14:


    nar "Contrary to her words, she looks around, still apparently wanting to say something."


translate English day4_0f20aff4:


    my "Um, [na2], umm... What is your relationship with the blonde girl?"


translate English day4_f75632bf:


    pl "What?"


translate English day4_49edaf33:


    nar "I feel my heart cease its beating, just for a moment." with sshake


translate English day4_54425142:


    pl "Why do you ask that?"


translate English day4_f18cc024:


    my "Why...? Well, I saw you... to... and..."


translate English day4_16191ad4:


    nar "Possibly surprised at me raising my voice, Maya looks down and starts mumbling."


translate English day4_fb0a0408:


    nar "And because I'm not familiar with how people talk in the capital, I can't really tell what she's saying."


translate English day4_e08ea579:


    pl "What? " with sshake


translate English day4_73192bca:


    extend "What did you see, Maya?!" with sshake


translate English day4_e386e840:


    nar "Perturbed, I ask her again. But then I realize that what I'm doing has scared her, so I take a deep breath to try and rationalize things inside my head."


translate English day4_bc2cce46:


    nar "It might just be a coincidence, but just then, something flies at me from behind." with hpunch


translate English day4_0b514db4:


    nar "It hits my back--and whatever it is, it's sticky and cold. Then it falls to the ground with a disappointing sound."


translate English day4_1feb74a9:


    nar "Naturally, I close my mouth again and look in the direction of the noise."


translate English day4_b2b6575c:


    nar "It's some kind of bright-red clump, with a yellow mass and dark blue blood vessels stuck to it. Blood seeps from it, staining the wooden floor."


translate English day4_16b3af29:


    nar "The scene from my dream flashes through my mind."


translate English day4_5d1103a8:


    nar "It's absurd, but as the embarrassment passes, I don't actually feel much confusion."


translate English day4_e6fd54ce:


    nar "Eventually, I hear a man's awful shriek, like nails on metal. " with sshake


translate English day4_450f5d9d:


    nar "It doesn't take long for me to realize that the horrific sound is coming from my own throat."


translate English day4_f4664270:


    nar "Several people nearby burst out laughing, appearing to revel in my shock."


translate English day4_7f9fde80:


    nar "I look up and see a few vaguely familiar Cleanup Department priests going past. I don't know them well."


translate English day4_df89f8d0:


    my "[na2]..."


translate English day4_334271ba:


    nar "Girls wearing thick face powder and boys wearing purposely baggy clothes have formed a pack of delinquents. "


translate English day4_6c23fb54:


    nar "They menacingly grin at me."


translate English day4_1f6c1d63:


    nar "I search my memory--I've definitely seen them before. They're the ones who were near Blondie."


translate English day4_cfa04074:


    nar "One of them meets my eyes, then raises his voice theatrically."


translate English day4_1b33e159:


    ex1 "Oh... Oh no! He saw us!"


translate English day4_eecf902d:


    nar "The guy next to him, clearly holding in a laugh at the first's joke, claps him on the shoulder."


translate English day4_385fe8c9:


    ex2 "Hey, what was that throw? Your aim sucks, man!"


translate English day4_9de5b2ae:


    nar "Fickle laughter."


translate English day4_2f611c31:


    ex1 "Ah, sorry! Wait... are you mad?"


translate English day4_219e8a8d:


    ex2 "Is he senile or something? Wow... Is this is first time seeing a mouse, or what?"


translate English day4_3111ecf7:


    nar "Amidst all the words flying back and forth, one person's voice catch my ears."


translate English day4_af6acdce:


    nar "A mouse? I look at \"it\" again. On the floor is a dead mouse, its fur snarled and its pupils clouded over."


translate English day4_1e544d23:


    nar "Definitely not what I saw a moment ago."


translate English day4_2644ba45:


    pl "W-Wait, but, just before, it..."


translate English day4_a807c81b:


    nar "Flustered, I grope around at my back, where it hit me. My hand comes back clean. Of course--no blood to speak of."


translate English day4_c5c90efb:


    nar "Then my dazed ears hear a voice cut through the tumult. That high, bouncing, sickening twang."


translate English day4_e9632202:


    lz2 "Ah, come on, quit bullying the poor new guy!"


translate English day4_96e35250:


    lz2 "Little [na2] is weak-hearted. You scared him!"


translate English day4_00c5731f:


    nar "As she grins, she joins in with the others' loud laughter. "


translate English day4_1200952c:


    nar "I don't even want to know what it is they talked about before this."


translate English day4_894747a1:


    ex2 "And Freckles's little sis is still with you, too! Are you going out or what?"


translate English day4_4402a877:


    ex1 "Hey! If you say stuff like that, your head might go flying! He's, you know! The Magic Department and all..."


translate English day4_aa13d33f:


    ex1 "Ah, Arne Alternata's..."


translate English day4_02555f15:


    nar "The one priest sticks out a pinky and gestures with it. I've never seen someone do that before, but I immediately realize what he means by it."


translate English day4_f845ec44:


    ex2 "Man, now I'm jealous. What'd a country bumpkin like him do to get that far? Did he yank his pants off in front of the princess or somethin'?"


translate English day4_4e9b4618:


    ex1 "Whoa. That's not just a minor love affair, huh?"


translate English day4_a813b16e:


    lz2 "Now isn't *that* something?"


translate English day4_310b636e:


    nar "Even more laughter rings out. Maya just stands there, frozen, with all the glares on her, unable to hide."


translate English day4_d229151c:


    nar "Their frivolous words make me feel faint. Did they know? How much? Everything? " with sshake


translate English day4_858f7f25:


    nar "Since when? Was I the only one who didn't know? Despite being directly involved? How many people knew about this?"


translate English day4_f1d1c963:


    nar "Eventually, I opened my mouth to ask the one question that made it through all the chaos in my head."


translate English day4_37843bcc:


    sc "What are you all doing here? Why aren't you working?" with hpunch


translate English day4_5bbaee27:


    ex2 "Whoa, it's the auxiliary bishop! I'm soooooo scared!"


translate English day4_ba065ec2:


    ex1 "I thought for a moment this dead mouse's mama walked in!"


translate English day4_994367b9:


    nar "Luckily, Securett's entrance immediately breaks them up."


translate English day4_31a93e8c:


    nar "As they scatter and head out of the room, he stops the blonde-haired girl."


translate English day4_5aed3bdb:


    sc "Get to the bishop's room. She has something else to say to you."


translate English day4_f4f04072:


    lz2 "You got it, bub."


translate English day4_6fb50638:


    nar "She leaves and the room is suddenly silent again like it was before, with only the three of us in it."


translate English day4_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day4_c2be7c48:


    sc "How long are you going to stand there? Ready yourselves."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_9422f135:


    pl "Um, hey, about the Magic Department..."


translate English day4_fafcaa21:


    "{nw}"


translate English day4_f08312f8:


    sc "...What about it?"


translate English day4_a80f03ef:


    nar "Neither of them seem surprised or questioning. "


translate English day4_55abd0c6:


    nar "The reason I transferred here, my engagement with Ar... I'm literally the only one who didn't know."


translate English day4_689bb4e6:


    my "[na2]... Are you okay...? Was that really your first time seeing a mouse?"


translate English day4_58214fcc:


    pl "N-No, of course not."


translate English day4_ba9f1648:


    pl "That was just... I guess I'm a little tired, I suppose."


translate English day4_783359b8:


    sc "That's because you go out at night despite not doing your job."


translate English day4_4eca0e98:


    pl "You sure know a lot about me."


translate English day4_574ed15b:


    pl "Just don't fall in love with me now~"


translate English day4_1c9c3ff3:


    sc "...Are you being serious?"


translate English day4_c66b2c19:


    pl "No, but you seem like you can take a joke. Seriously, dude."


translate English day4_44ed20f2:


    pl "And yet for everything you say, you always come rushing to help out whenever something happens."


translate English day4_3bd5a501:


    sc "I wasn't coming to rescue you."


translate English day4_0e300c70:


    my "But I'm really glad you came, Cue... Thank you."


translate English day4_0384a53b:


    sc "Sigh... You don't need to bother with people like them every single time. They'll stop coming after a month or so of work."


translate English day4_6951de72:


    my "Oh, so you can quit the Cleanup Department...?"


translate English day4_e18d26cf:


    pl "Wait, for real? Huh. I thought I was the only one who'd ever be switching departments."


translate English day4_77791284:


    sc "..."


translate English day4_af7732f2:


    nar "Once again, he shuts his mouth the moment things get a little awkward. Maya sees that and opens her mouth to speak first."


translate English day4_cab303df:


    nar "As she breaks the silence, I gratefully put in a few words, too."


translate English day4_cd145299:


    my "Um, so Cue, how long have you been working in the Cleanup Department?"


translate English day4_232647bf:


    pl "Oh, yeah! You're really passionate about this, but you've been rotting away in the disposal team for how many years now? You've gotta aim higher, my guy!"


translate English day4_b7a53b28:


    nar "He stays silent, as always. I clap him on his slender back. Maya gently lowers her voice and starts twiddling her thumbs."


translate English day4_fc2623a8:


    my "You're so smart, I bet you could be in the Academics Department..."


translate English day4_b58f3872:


    my "Ah, I guess if I were able to change departments, I'd want to go to the Health Department."


translate English day4_bf16b7fb:


    my "I really like being able to help people, so..."


translate English day4_26e0ca43:


    pl "What?! Maya, that would really suit you! You're kind of like an angel already!"


translate English day4_5faabd68:


    pl "If you were in the Health Department, I'd come hang out every single day and bring you an apple."


translate English day4_765de245:


    my "Thanks, [na2]. I hope you do well in the Magic Department, too."


translate English day4_8ccaa6bf:


    pl "R-Right, the Magic Department..."


translate English day4_349ab567:


    nar "All the stuff from before starts to get to me again. Sensing my discomfort, Maya's face clouds over."


translate English day4_b12536ae:


    my "Oh... S-Sorry..."


translate English day4_0abb4b83:


    pl "No, I was just thinking a little about the Magic Department... I wonder what kind of place it is."


translate English day4_67bf4720:


    my "I mean, they do exorcisms and stuff..."


translate English day4_d6b687fb:


    pl "Exercise? I can do that!"


translate English day4_0984684c:


    my "...That's not what I said."


translate English day4_d0b68c72:


    pl "Haha! I was just kidding."


translate English day4_63708a64:


    my "Come on..."


translate English day4_b093b6e9:


    pl "I didn't realize exorcists were different from regular clergy."


translate English day4_f3d29df2:


    pl "I mean, even WE get called \"father\" and such in town, right?"


translate English day4_01a823a0:


    my "The Cleaning Department aren't clergy or exorcists, [na2]. We're just--"


translate English day4_39ad7ed7:


    sc "We're just the cleaners."


translate English day4_705ed5ec:


    nar "Maya's shoulders jump at Securett's sudden, casual words."


translate English day4_e8f334a2:


    nar "But that's all. He doesn't react any more than that; he just brushes my hand off his back and walks down the hallway."


translate English day4_7f87b153:


    nar "If a cleaner is all he thought he was, why was Securett still working his butt off in a place like this?"


translate English day4_98f3c30e:


    nar "If that weak-looking bishop heard him say that, she'd probably start crying."


translate English day4_5c0e3239:


    nar "With the conversation cut off, Maya and I can only awkwardly follow Securett to work."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_21f5e12e:


    "\n We follow Securett to a path that's very different from the kind we've seen at the temple or in the residential areas."


translate English day4_ced41186:


    "I'm not sure how to put it: the air feels different or something. It's not a place I would have assumed we'd be working in."


translate English day4_42f4613d:


    "A thick fog hangs between the trees, obstructing our vision. The path we walk is unpaved. My feet get caught on corners of stones or tree roots every time I take a step. I nearly trip several times."


translate English day4_725dd2b3:


    et "Securett is headed deeper into the forest. Though it's morning, the fog is hanging strangely low."


translate English day4_9d3ef999:



    nvl clear
    "\n The two of us trail behind him. Since we can't see more than a few inches in front of us, though, we're flailing our limbs for the most part. Securett, however, is having almost no trouble finding--and keeping--his footing."


translate English day4_d2cce551:


    "If we lose our way here, we'll probably be lost for a considerable amount of time."


translate English day4_9d857523:


    "As if in agreement, Maya and I keep our mouths tightly shut and eventually cling to Securett's arm and shoulder. That's the only way we'll get anywhere safe and sound."


translate English day4_34b7813d:


    et "Meanwhile, I'm not exactly a happy camper. How do they even expect people to do this kind of work? At the same time, though, I can tell the boy in front of us comes here pretty frequently."


translate English day4_20f59771:



    nvl clear
    "\n About twenty minutes pass after the last sign of anyone else. Finally, the three of us stop in front of a small hut."


translate English day4_882e9df9:


    "The air around the hut feels clearer than the path we came here on. It's like being in the eye of the storm--although I'm not sure that expression applies here."


translate English day4_c31891e0:


    et "Securett takes a key ring out of his inside pocket and starts counting off the keys. He chooses one from the middle and uses it to open the door."


translate English day4_15b1ea21:



    nvl clear
    "\n When we go inside, we see that someone's been taking good care of the place. {w}However, there isn't any furniture to speak of--only some boxes of various sizes."


translate English day4_a5338f11:


    "At the very least, I don't choke on the musty odor of wet wood or slip on any rotting, crushed-up flesh lying on the floor."


translate English day4_6e8240b2:


    "Securett selects a relatively large box and fishes around in it. He comes out with heavy-looking metal tools and gives one to each of us."


translate English day4_68cc5f64:


    et "One is a dagger a little longer than my palm. The other is a gun."


translate English day4_87253020:


    sc "Take these."


translate English day4_924a35a1:


    pl "What is this place?"


translate English day4_30ced021:


    sc "A battle station. One of several, in fact."


translate English day4_b37c2555:


    pl "Isn't there already a storehouse in the workplace? Why does it have not one, but a bunch of battle stations?"


translate English day4_a74cb602:


    sc "Well... I don't know why, to be honest."


translate English day4_e8bbee77:


    pl "What?"


translate English day4_59327ab1:


    sc "I think only qualified priests are told about it--qualifications of which I still don't have."


translate English day4_f49f068b:


    nar "Something's going on. Hearing the term \"battle station\" while being given weapons really makes the whole \"I'm employed at a temple\" thing have more impact."


translate English day4_6ce3020a:


    pl "Okay, then why did you give us these?"


translate English day4_21c239a7:


    sc "Because we're going somewhere dangerous for newcomers like you. This is actually our standard loadout when we go out to \"clean.\""


translate English day4_93f35dec:


    pl "Well, forgive me if I'm not exactly thanking you for receiving a *weapon*."


translate English day4_21b94690:


    my "Wow... This is the first time I've ever seen a gun."


translate English day4_26784ae4:


    nar "Securett frowns and sighs. He doesn't seem to like talking for very long."


translate English day4_814e7237:


    sc "I won't say this again, so listen carefully."


translate English day4_fa9381ff:


    sc "We're about to enter the Pestis Field."


translate English day4_7712586a:


    pl "Pestis?"


translate English day4_27ebd1c8:


    my "Field...?"


translate English day4_c9c677f7:


    sc "...I know you said you came from outside the capital, but do you not even know what the pestis is?"


translate English day4_a7149beb:


    pl "...Mgh..."


translate English day4_7cd3e67c:


    sc "Sigh..."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_2c2b5f5a:


    "\n The pestis--an overwhelming power that humans simply cannot oppose."


translate English day4_86df250b:


    "A generic name for a mysterious phenomena that even modern science hasn't been able to fully explain."


translate English day4_801f311d:


    "\"About two thousand years ago,\na world-altering catacylsm occurred.\""


translate English day4_ad80bdcf:


    "\"After the pestis, men began appearing with strange wounds on them. They received a message from God containing the necessary strength and information to rebuild their lands.\""


translate English day4_f26c920f:


    et "That's something I'm pretty sure I've heard before from the adults in the village."


translate English day4_3c1c8547:



    nvl clear
    "\n Securett begins to tell us about it as he performs his maintenance on the blade he holds."


translate English day4_3682f1a5:


    "It's all new to me. Well, not exactly new, per se."


translate English day4_b8cf6558:


    "The people back home would sometimes look to the sky and perform rituals. They didn't happen on specific days--they'd just happen, and when the time came near,"


translate English day4_84b91721:


    "the villagers would drag me to a small altar space and not let me sleep. I would have to spend the night counting the stains on the walls."


translate English day4_8c904477:


    et "And when the sun rose, everyone would gather and we'd have a funeral service for someone. Maybe someone like a friend I'd always talked with until just the day before or the lady next door who always said good morning to me."


translate English day4_947f4b5c:



    nvl clear
    "\n I wasn't alone in this. {w}Until I became an adult, I never knew what those days were or why we did the rituals,"


translate English day4_2f4021cf:


    extend " but I definitely remember how the adults would get red in the face and start shouting about someone arriving."


translate English day4_fc83ab37:


    "Securett's explanation is similar to that."


translate English day4_b4b7900d:


    et "The pestis, stigmata--both are just unfamiliar terms for things I already knew about. That's probably what everyone in the capital calls them."


translate English day4_1386e2ca:


    sc "The Pestis's field is what is obstructing our vision. To put it simply, this is a big area in which the Pestis can occur."


translate English day4_7022323e:


    sc "...I'm sure even you two noticed the veil of fog on the path on the way here."


translate English day4_32f9fa6b:


    nar "He really does just ignore people, doesn't he..."


translate English day4_83eff57f:


    my "The fog was drifting the whole time..."


translate English day4_8dbad615:


    sc "That's because the field, too, always flows, based on several external factors."


translate English day4_ce4b8eee:


    nar "I glare at him unhappily. Our eyes meet, but Securett ignores me and continues talking."


translate English day4_5dfd82d4:


    sc "Do either of you know how a fishhook works?"


translate English day4_e0da5e10:


    my "A fish gets caught on a hook, and then it gets stuck on the barb on the other side of it, so it can't wiggle free, right?"


translate English day4_8c48ddc6:


    sc "Very good. Getting caught on the hook is one thing, but..."


translate English day4_80d29453:


    sc "when the fish tries to pull itself off, it *painfully* rips itself apart."


translate English day4_6949ccdc:


    sc "The pestis essentially works like that. The more you go against the direction its field flows in, the more painful it is."


translate English day4_601759b8:


    pl "Doesn't that mean if you could predict its direction in advance, the pestis wouldn't happen at all?"


translate English day4_cd9b78c2:


    sc "Theoretically, yes. That's why the Academics Department does so much research on how the Pestis flows."


translate English day4_2e1bc8ea:


    sc "...But that's beyond you two."


translate English day4_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day4_a2359111:


    sc "Slight dizziness and nausea. You've felt them before while working, haven't you?"


translate English day4_e467a795:


    sc "It can be even worse--blood spurting from your orifices, permanent loss of all your senses, mental abnormalities, all kinds of other injuries, just to name a few."


translate English day4_10b52070:


    my "Ahhh..."


translate English day4_da9f18ec:


    nar "I'm surprised he can say all that stuff with a straight face."


translate English day4_8e9dcd9f:


    sc "That's all the normal stuff, anyway. "


translate English day4_8df390fe:


    sc "When the \"true\" pestis comes, diseases can spread and wipe out entire villages. In some instances, the ground simply decays. It happens a lot."


translate English day4_55a68a19:


    sc "But the temple is prepared for that."


translate English day4_857e4d43:


    my "So the Academics Department researches pestes, the Magic Department confronts it, and the Health Department supports the injured."


translate English day4_73b86ddc:


    my "Cue, that's amazing... It's so cool that you know all these complicated things..."


translate English day4_80c65667:


    sc "Yeah, well..."


translate English day4_5dae5181:


    nar "I mumble a single thought to myself: Is that why all the land outside towns like my home and the capital is desolate and decayed?"


translate English day4_0847e6ca:


    nar "When I was getting ready to leave for the capital,"


translate English day4_f7a87eb7:


    nar "the village elders talked my ears off about not ever straying from the path they set for me."


translate English day4_56522a48:


    nar "Was that all for a reason? Is it possible the journey I took was actually a horrendously frightful one?"


translate English day4_18ec40f3:


    sc "...This is all common knowledge. The pestis can take on several other forms."


translate English day4_43f10aba:


    sc "You each only have two stigmata, so you'll never have to face very dangerous varieties of it, but it's good to know in any case."


translate English day4_51c45969:


    sc "Understand? Let's head out."


translate English day4_1ae164a9:


    nar "Almost dismissively, Securett tosses us the metallic items. "


translate English day4_896332bf:


    nar "He was right--all this horrible stuff wasn't quite sinking in for us yet."


translate English day4_51b87f57:


    nar "Even if that sort of incident occured, it was always to someone else. I've never been directly, personally harmed by the pestis."


translate English day4_2c33cc2e:


    nar "Maya and I exchange glances. She looks discouraged; she's probably thinking the same thing as me."


translate English day4_c564b99e:


    nar "And so, the three of us leave the battle station behind and head back out into the fog."


translate English day4_e5692709:


    sc "...Stop."


translate English day4_d3ce1a1d:


    my "Huh?"


translate English day4_3a659340:


    sc "This is where we enter the pestis's area of effect."


translate English day4_5c10abde:


    sc "Make absolutely sure you don't turn around until I say otherwise."


translate English day4_3da84c2e:


    sc "Also, if you hear anyone through the fog, it's an illusion. Don't respond or acknowledge it."


translate English day4_668d523b:


    pl "What happens if we do?"


translate English day4_f8575379:


    sc "I don't know. They never told me."


translate English day4_f3aa92ab:


    pl "What the heck?"


translate English day4_dc2a16af:


    sc "But I've seen people cough up blood or be unable to see straight for a month. "


translate English day4_3172818e:


    sc "And sometimes they just disappear and never come back."


translate English day4_599eed70:


    sc "If you're that curious, I won't stop you from finding out for yourselves, but..."


translate English day4_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "......"


translate English day4_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_38a5c448:


    "\n I could swear we've been following Securett for a while now, but the fog is making it feel like time isn't passing at all."


translate English day4_bbf6e664:


    et "Even just keeping my eyes forward is difficult. His rule not to look back is bothering me more than I thought it would. My senses are honed so much that even the tiniest sensations cause me to jump."


translate English day4_b84bf240:



    nvl clear
    "\n Securett told us our job for today was to retrieve the remains of a human who was taken away by one of the Lost."


translate English day4_e756c24e:


    "The forest is empty, though houses do stand along its edge. According to him, the Lost that aren't under the pestis's effects use the proximity to attack people at night."


translate English day4_f9f7f44e:


    "After Maya and I went back, the disposal team's main mission would apparently be to hunt for the Lost that's to blame."


translate English day4_bebed625:


    et "If we were attacked in this fog, especially after the sun went down, it wouldn't matter how strong I was--I wouldn't be able to compete with it. {w}It makes sense to me."


translate English day4_b47ebfbe:



    nvl clear
    "\n And there are probably other members of the disposal team around the area too, obscured by the ever-present fog."


translate English day4_c261711c:


    "Sometimes, I'll hear something next to me. I usually can't tell if it's a teammate or just an illusion."


translate English day4_ee2833cb:


    et "Maya has tripped over dried tree roots and shrieked a few times by now, so we ended up linking arms and taking extra care where we step."


translate English day4_61b2d617:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"...\""


translate English day4_4cb869a6:


    "The only thing that stands out to me in this fog is the presence of that short, frightened girl, holding fast to my sleeve and trembling."


translate English day4_2cc5b480:


    "I can hear her breathing, ringing like a pounding in my head. The feeling of her small fingers is really getting to me."


translate English day4_ac2b1b3f:


    "I see the downy hair on her arm being blown by the wind, which raises the hairs on the back of my neck."


translate English day4_c29d7c9e:


    "If I zone out now, the pestis will surely claim me as another victim. To prevent it, I keep changing where I'm looking, but"


translate English day4_03f344f0:


    et "cruelly, the sound of my rapidly beating heart and pulse keeps sounding like Maya, and so I end up peering at her face several times. My face is hot. I'm dizzy. Maybe the pestis is affecting me already and I haven't realized."


translate English day4_c8d6bda6:


    my "Um..."


translate English day4_e0b9f1b3:


    pl "Wh-What is it?! Maya, is anything wrong?!"


translate English day4_2bff9204:


    nar "My voice cracks badly."


translate English day4_d749906e:


    nar "I immediately feel like shutting my mouth and clamming up, but she shakes her head without a word."


translate English day4_81950594:


    my "...It's reassuring to know you're here, [na2]."


translate English day4_4b916bfa:


    nar "I can't make out her face very well through this thick fog. But to think a precious creature like her is a human like me!"


translate English day4_407de414:


    pl "An angel..."


translate English day4_d3ce1a1d_1:


    my "Huh?"


translate English day4_f5478038:


    pl "God-given cuteness..."


translate English day4_d6375423:


    my "Oh, come on..."


translate English day4_cfe4e5c2:


    sc "If you have time to be making idle chatter, then you have enough time to pay attention to the ground as well. Focus."


translate English day4_9b08748e:


    nar "As expected, Securett is always one to dump cold water all over a good mood."


translate English day4_cf4d1328:


    nar "He said that in his usual unfriendly tone, without turning around."


translate English day4_7dfd9292:


    nar "Normally, I'd have thought he was a creep, but the situation being what it is, I sort of understand his tendency to be curt."


translate English day4_bde7656e:


    nar "Securett isn't walking very slowly, "


translate English day4_8b4ba5c4:


    nar "but if he spots anything of note on the difficult-to-see ground, he immediately picks it up, examines it, and puts it in his bag."


translate English day4_3a3d4e27:


    nar "I can see other things in the bag, too--human fingers, teeth."


translate English day4_3456f4fe:


    pl "Haha, sorry, sorry!"


translate English day4_23e2ba3c:


    pl "I can barely see the ground with this crazy fog in the way. I couldn't search for anything if I tried. How are you doing such a good job of it?"


translate English day4_44b590e9:


    sc "...You get better with practice."


translate English day4_8c268d86:


    pl "Want help carrying the bag?"


translate English day4_4839d8af:


    sc "No."


translate English day4_92ddc164:


    pl "Oh, come on now!"


translate English day4_80c55166:


    nar "Following Securett without getting lost has been the only thing we've been able to do this entire time."


translate English day4_50e9fc22:


    nar "I'm really getting tired of all the monotony, so I want to keep this conversation with him going."


translate English day4_7f15309d:


    nar "Otherwise, I might start getting a little scared of this strange fog-in-the-woods situation that I can't wrap my below-average intelligence around."


translate English day4_c6913f2c:


    pl "Anyway, aside from that curse you said about not turning around..."


translate English day4_9eb42af3:


    pl "and this fog making it totally impossible to see, nothing here seems very dangerous. Why'd you give me a blade?"


translate English day4_11581c62:


    sc "Well--"


translate English day4_8e629a92:


    nar "Wind conveniently blows through, covering up the sound of his voice."


translate English day4_4f4872ee:


    pl "...Oh, sorry. What was that?"


translate English day4_7691a6a0:


    sc "...I think that when we're done today, you should study up on how people in the capital speak."


translate English day4_87835d3d:


    pl "No, I just didn't hear you! Don't you think the wind here is a little strong?"


translate English day4_c990ea89:


    nar "Securett sighs in resignation and points at the gun Maya is carrying."


translate English day4_8e41d66e:


    sc "The temple made that."


translate English day4_2444157c:


    sc "The Lost may be a common sight when it comes to pestis phenomena, but normal methods aren't enough to deal with them."


translate English day4_385214a4:


    sc "You have to behead them in one stroke... And we can't expect you newbies to be able to do that with any ease."


translate English day4_8c35b6ad:


    sc "That gun has been enchanted with a spell. With it, even people with just two stigmata like you can at least slow them down."


translate English day4_0d58d8d8:


    sc "...Though you would need to run for your lives after doing so."


translate English day4_529eeff0:


    my "Aww..."


translate English day4_4f590e8c:


    sc "The Lost come out at night a lot, but nobody knows when they start appearing or start wandering."


translate English day4_217c1510:


    sc "So, we all have to protect ourselves. After all, I'm the one who will suffer if there's more corpses to deal with."


translate English day4_446bb597:


    sc "...Also, that dagger is just a dagger."


translate English day4_aba2730c:


    nar "The way Securett keeps pointing out how I \"only\" have two stigmata is really wounding my pride."


translate English day4_06fef836:


    nar "But just as I'm stewing over that, I realize that Securett's explanations today have been longer and have sounded more melancholy than normal."


translate English day4_b6ee9f50:


    nar "I'm still hearing that wind, too. It's awfully annoying."


translate English day4_d4e1e218:


    nar "I'm about to vent all these pent-up feelings at Securett that I've been bottling up but then Maya thankfully opens her mouth to speak."


translate English day4_8449fc44:


    nar "In the end, his ears never hear my complaints."


translate English day4_c8b63dec:


    my "Umm, Cue, what's good about having more stigmata?"


translate English day4_6ccb7908:


    my "That is, w-well... At the monastery, they just said more stigmata means you have more sacred power, but... "


translate English day4_4f5b948e:


    my "Now that you mentioned it... I was hoping you could explain it to me."


translate English day4_77791284_1:


    sc "..."


translate English day4_5ff90fee:


    sc "Look."


translate English day4_543d7c9a:


    nar "Securett stops. "


translate English day4_2c0c50f3:


    nar "He brings both arms to his left side so that we can see him better from behind."


translate English day4_8e3e3a96:


    nar "Then, he angles the dagger he's holding in one hand upwards."


translate English day4_f33e5d00:


    nar "He then lifts his other hand on top of it, opening his palm up to cover the blade--like he's about to stab himself through the center."


translate English day4_133744c3:


    nar "But he wiggles his open palm a little as if proud of how dangerous it looks."


translate English day4_5b41c2d6:


    sc "If I swung my palm down, what do you think would happen?"


translate English day4_5b4b82f8:


    pl "I mean, you'd stab yourself! What are you doing, you idiot?!"


translate English day4_e322b5dc:


    sc "It's just an example. Now, what if I swung down a hammer instead of my bare hand?"


translate English day4_19fa213f:


    my "H-Hmm... It might knock the dagger out of your hand..."


translate English day4_4c7d54b9:


    sc "Correct. Well, halfway."


translate English day4_6c1dd740:


    sc "This is the difference between someone with stigmata and someone without."


translate English day4_22be21ab:


    sc "The more stigmata appear on your body, the more you can get away with relatively minor injuries if you go against the pestis's direction...and the stronger its flow's influence is on you."


translate English day4_64a1a29c:


    pl "But I thought having more stigmata makes you stronger."


translate English day4_a2bec44a:


    sc "Basically, but you have the cause and effect backwards. It's not that you're stronger because you have more stigmata--it's that the stronger you are, the more stigmata will appear on you."


translate English day4_d2c8c3ad:


    pl "Whoa. So if I get stronger, I might get more stigmata."


translate English day4_708990c3:


    sc "Who can say... I've never seen anyone acquire more than they had at birth."


translate English day4_f9999b1c:


    nar "Securett speaks clearly and bluntly, like he's ridiculing my hopes and dreams, then opens his narrowed eyes a little bit and adds:"


translate English day4_acf81855:


    sc "...Nor has history ever witnessed such a thing."


translate English day4_04005ca0:


    nar "Then he starts moving again. He must be done talking."


translate English day4_76135f9d:


    nar "But I stay where I am, unable to move. Because just as Securett finished speaking, I heard a woman laugh."


translate English day4_f73f4953:


    nar "A chill runs down my spine. I get goosebumps, like I've noticed something I wasn't supposed to. "


translate English day4_5760bbd2:


    nar "I now know what all those random noises I've been hearing are: I assumed it was the wind."


translate English day4_ba471c17:


    my "[na2]?"


translate English day4_a5af336f:


    pl "Uh... Uh? Oh, sorry. What's been going on with me lately...?"


translate English day4_4223b766:


    nar "I collect myself and go after Securett, still supporting Maya. "


translate English day4_26843db1:


    nar "You'd think that after walking this far we'd be close to the end, but it honestly seems like he's going even deeper in."


translate English day4_4cc1caf7:


    nar "The woman's laughter reverberates inside my head, growing ever louder, pounding inside my skull."


translate English day4_586699ad:


    nar "The giggling continues to grow, and just as I think it's over, it bursts into uproarious laughter, becoming even clearer in my mind."


translate English day4_0ef2e326:


    nar "Maya looks between me and our surroundings, her eyes full of worry."


translate English day4_a44a683a:


    pl "Ugh, guh..."


translate English day4_859511b4:


    my "[na2], are you alright?"


translate English day4_a9bcd157:


    nar "Dozens of crying voices echo in my head. I can't tell which sounds are real and which are fake."


translate English day4_c303b9e6:


    nar "I can't tell Maya about this, since she doesn't hear it. That's my situation. I can only moan, steadily getting dizzier and dizzier."


translate English day4_4610e18b:


    nar "Each one of the shouts sounds like it's saying its own thing, but I can't make any of them out because of the roaring wind."


translate English day4_df96e699:


    nar "But then, one voice pierces clearly through to my ears."


translate English day4_d68ea3ec:


    nar "\"Please... Somebody, help!\""


translate English day4_f34188cc:


    nar "That voice wakes me up. I turn to the side, in its direction. That one wasn't an illusion. I have no objective evidence, but I'm certain of it all the same."


translate English day4_e7c42531:


    nar "Somebody within the fog needs help."


translate English day4_2f850ca6:


    nar "The scream was vivid and desperate and *definitely* human. This area is very hilly: I have to go save whoever it is..."


translate English day4_9a8ebfd5:


    nar "Securett's remarks about the pestis's curse flow through my mind."


translate English day4_850b3bff:


    pl "...Maya."


translate English day4_7c27ff69:


    nar "I give Maya's hand a tug and bring it to Securett's back. I'm afraid she'd fall over if I simply let go."


translate English day4_c1778f86:


    pl "Sorry. I'll be right back."


translate English day4_cbac79b1:


    my "[na2]...?!"


translate English day4_96f43e44:


    nar "I let go of her hand and turn towards the voice, then dash away."


translate English day4_ea747562:


    sc "Hey, wait! Where are you going?! Hey! [na]!"


translate English day4_48832db3:


    sc "Damn it! The field is stronger that way! It's dangerous...!"


translate English day4_d6dce235:


    my "C-Cue, what should we do?!"


translate English day4_77bdad79:


    sc "Dammit...!"


translate English day4_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_a214dfe5:


    "\n I've always been an athletic person. {w}Having to prop up someone else is one thing, but everything changes when I'm free to move about the way I want to."


translate English day4_a5786588:


    "Maybe my athleticism gives me the kind of reckless courage I need to do something this rash. I run, kicking off of the corners of rocks and using fallen trees as stepping stones."


translate English day4_1fe0cee2:


    "As the fog thickens, the crying voice grows equally clearer. I see the worst-case scenario in my mind's eye."


translate English day4_25cf1cb5:


    "Someone in the disposal team probably slipped, fell onto a slanted path, and tumbled down a hill. Now, they're probably isolated from the rest of us within the fog."


translate English day4_7ab457be:


    "Even if they were lucky, their options are likely limited now. They might be bleeding terribly from the effects of the pestis's curse. "


translate English day4_1045e44b:


    et "Maybe there are too many stranded people for me to handle."


translate English day4_c9e5af9c:



    nvl clear
    "\n But worrying about it like this won't change anything. {w}I can't overlook someone in need. Plus, my personal sense of justice tells me they're both still alive."


translate English day4_d7ac8c09:


    "I have to make it in time. I have to! As the wailing voice grows even clearer, it begins to shift into a bestial cry."


translate English day4_a8237770:


    "I run for a while and eventually, my feet start to throb. I think the tree branches I'm grazing are tearing the skin from them."


translate English day4_0ea99cea:


    "I'm not used to wild, unkempt trails like this. It feels like I'm running around the same place over and over."


translate English day4_d58c2928:


    "But I have to keep running. The voice is crying out for help too sincerely for me to do otherwise."


translate English day4_a1261285:



    nvl clear
    et "\n I think it's somewhere around here..."


translate English day4_057a6cbf:


    "I stop and gasp for breath. The voice is so vivid and clear, it sounds like it's right next to me."


translate English day4_4c026515:


    "I glance around as I carefully take my next few steps forward."


translate English day4_b806d349:


    "\"Hey! Is someone out there?!\""


translate English day4_ef74c474:


    "No response."


translate English day4_1d917212:


    et "......"


translate English day4_8e5fadde:



    nvl clear
    "\n I sharpen my senses, trying to catch even the softest noise as it slips by. But I can't hear anything."


translate English day4_fad45c57:


    "Suddenly, I see Securett's face in my mind, warning me about the pestis and its effects."


translate English day4_0332f1b7:


    "Have I been altered by it? Is this how it went for all the people who disappeared in the night back home?"


translate English day4_1e4985f0:


    et "I run out of energy to move. A sense of despondency, not fear, crawls up my spine."


translate English day4_a75088ff:



    nvl clear
    "\n But it doesn't last long, because suddenly, a cry pierces the terrible silence--right next to where I'm standing."


translate English day4_ab9343b0:


    "Startled, I take my dagger out reflexively. I face where I heard the voice and carefully look around."


translate English day4_b65f056c:


    "Someone's definitely there. And that person has to be the one who was begging for my help."


translate English day4_e2a27e12:


    et "But I can't help but panic. Because that person, while they're a person, they're... They're too..."


translate English day4_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day4_b6eb7fb7:


    "\n {space=-3}What I see is too profane to be called \"human\" in the least."


translate English day4_55ece3b1:


    "{space=-3}What looks at first like a blood clot clearly has no sanity to its form, no matter how I look at it. {w}Rips and tears have mutilated up the skin's surface."


translate English day4_297b88b8:


    "Broken bones pierce and protrude from flesh--most likely an injury from falling down this hill."


translate English day4_0f130980:


    "But even then, the arms and legs are extremely swollen and colored a deep, dark blue. Two blood clots, each slightly larger than a clenched fist, cling to the part of their body that must be their face."


translate English day4_36496ab6:


    "I don't understand what they are at first, but when the skin still attached to the blood clots blinks and I see the human irises within, every hair on my body immediately stands on end."


translate English day4_fe9311a2:


    et "Yet more blackened clots protrude from all over the body, pulsating to the fierce beating of a heart. I refuse to believe this is a human--I simply refuse."


translate English day4_fc2a75a0:



    nvl clear
    "\n It screams in unintelligible words, writhing and rolling atop the vomit and excreta produced from itself."


translate English day4_2b1ef20b:


    "It doesn't appear to be able to see or hear anything."


translate English day4_c0d70fae:


    "I can say nothing before this confounding sight. I can still hear cries echoing throughout the deep forest."


translate English day4_f04c4d76:


    "After not speaking for a while, I finally move one foot and slowly take a step forwards. I begin to move deeper, little by little, towards the sound."


translate English day4_62116c8b:


    "I'd be lying if I said I wasn't terrified after this."


translate English day4_fdd6ab7e:


