    "The bishop's voice is dreadfully flat as she begins to chant a prayer informing us of execution. The fact that it sounds just like she did this morning makes me feel faint."


translate English day4_night_54da9740:


    "Everything that's become normal at this point mixes with the abnormal sight in front of me. My mind is nowhere near able to accept it all."


translate English day4_night_4d67f593:


    "I couldn't make out the rest of the prayer, but it's apparently over, because the bishop crosses back over the threshold with one robed man."


translate English day4_night_8587c69b:


    et "Only filth now remains in that space she vanished from."


translate English day4_night_cb04da00:



    nvl clear
    "\n Her shoulders, so thin now they look like they might fall off, sway, as though unable to endure the mounting pressure. "


